"Location" text,
"Name" text,
"Capacity" int,
"Highest" int,
"Lowest" int,
"Average" int,
PRIMARY KEY ("Stadium_ID")
)

"Singer_ID" int,
"Name" text,
"Country" text,
"Song_Name" text,
"Song_release_year" text,
"Age" int,
"Is_male" bool,

)

)
